DEFENDANT IN APPROXIMATELY 10,800 LAWSUITS, WHICH INCLUDE

APPROXIMATELY 26,800 PLAINTIFF GROUPS, ALLEGING PERSONAL

INJURIES RESULTING FROM THE USE OF

VIOXX

, AND IN

