ZOCOR,

THE COMPANYS STATIN FOR MODIFYING CHOLESTEROL WHICH

LOST U.S. MARKET EXCLUSIVITY IN 2006, LOWER SALES OF

VASOTEC/VASERETIC

FOR THE TREATMENT OF HYPERTENSION

AND/OR

