CONSIDERED WHEN IT PREVIOUSLY ESTABLISHED RESERVES FOR THE

VIOXX

LITIGATION. SOME OF THE SIGNIFICANT FACTORS

CONSIDERED IN THE REVIEW OF THE

VIOXX

RESERVE WERE AS

