DEVELOPMENT OF THE COMPANYS LEGAL DEFENSE STRATEGY AND

STRUCTURE IN LIGHT OF THE SCOPE OF THE

VIOXX

LITIGATION,

INCLUDING THE SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT AND THE EXPECTATION THAT

