CASES BEING BROUGHT AGAINST THE COMPANY; THE COSTS AND OUTCOMES

OF COMPLETED TRIALS AND THE MOST CURRENT INFORMATION REGARDING

ANTICIPATED TIMING, PROGRESSION, AND RELATED COSTS OF PRE-TRIAL

