DENIED THE MOTION IN JUNE 2008 AND CLOSED THE CASE. PLAINTIFFS

HAVE APPEALED JUDGE CHESLERS DECISION TO THE UNITED STATES

COURT OF APPEALS FOR THE THIRD CIRCUIT.

