PRIMARILY OF ACCOUNTS RECEIVABLE. THE PARTNERSHIP DOES NOT

NORMALLY REQUIRE COLLATERAL OR OTHER SECURITY TO SUPPORT CREDIT

SALES. BAD DEBTS FOR THE YEARS ENDED

